# Interim Data
# ============
# Intermediate cleaning stages, generated automatically by pipeline.
# Path: $NANO_DATA_ROOT/interim/
# See config/paths.yml for full path definitions.
#
# Contents:
#   ecg_filtered/   <- Bandpass-filtered ECG signals
#   rpeaks/         <- Detected R-peak indices and IBI series
#   quality_flags/  <- Per-window quality flags (accepted/rejected)
#   redcap_merged/  <- Pre-merge REDCap + physio data frames
